import React from 'react';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import {
  AppBar,
  Toolbar,
  Button,
  Box,
  Typography,
  Menu,
  MenuItem,
  IconButton,
} from '@mui/material';
import { Facebook, Twitter, Instagram } from '@mui/icons-material';
import MenuIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Menu';
import ExpandMoreIcon from '@mui/icons-material/ExpandMore';

const Home = () => {
  const [anchorEl, setAnchorEl] = React.useState(null);

  const handleDropdownOpen = (event) => {
    setAnchorEl(event.currentTarget);
  };

  const handleDropdownClose = () => {
    setAnchorEl(null);
  };

  return (
    <Box className="background-animation" sx={{ minHeight: '100vh', overflow: 'auto' }}>
      {/* Navigation Bar */}
      <AppBar position="sticky" sx={{ bgcolor: '#1976d2' }}>
        <Toolbar>
          <Box
            component="img"
            src={`${process.env.PUBLIC_URL}/logo.svg`}
            alt="JobWings Logo"
            sx={{
              height: 40,
              width: 40,
              mr: 2,
            }}
          />
          <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
            JobWings
          </Typography>
          <Link to="/" style={{ textDecoration: 'none', color: '#fff', marginRight: '1rem' }}>
            <Button color="inherit">Home</Button>
          </Link>
          <Link to="#about" style={{ textDecoration: 'none', color: '#fff', marginRight: '1rem' }}>
            <Button color="inherit">About</Button>
          </Link>
          <Link
            to="#resume-templates"
            style={{ textDecoration: 'none', color: '#fff', marginRight: '1rem' }}
          >
            <Button color="inherit">Resume Templates</Button>
          </Link>
          <Link to="#jobs" style={{ textDecoration: 'none', color: '#fff', marginRight: '1rem' }}>
            <Button color="inherit">Jobs</Button>
          </Link>
          <Link to="#contact" style={{ textDecoration: 'none', color: '#fff' }}>
            <Button color="inherit">Contact</Button>
          </Link>

          {/* Dropdown for Login */}
          <Button
            color="inherit"
            onClick={handleDropdownOpen}
            endIcon={<ExpandMoreIcon />}
            sx={{ ml: 2 }}
          >
            Login
          </Button>
          <Menu anchorEl={anchorEl} open={Boolean(anchorEl)} onClose={handleDropdownClose}>
            <MenuItem onClick={handleDropdownClose}>
              <Link to="/login/user" style={{ textDecoration: 'none', color: '#000' }}>
                User Login
              </Link>
            </MenuItem>
            <MenuItem onClick={handleDropdownClose}>
              <Link to="/login/recruiter" style={{ textDecoration: 'none', color: '#000' }}>
                Recruiter Login
              </Link>
            </MenuItem>
          </Menu>
        </Toolbar>
      </AppBar>

      {/* Sections */}
      <Box
        id="about"
        sx={{
          minHeight: '100vh',
          display: 'flex',
          flexDirection: 'column',
          alignItems: 'center',
          justifyContent: 'center',
          bgcolor: '#f5f5f5',
          padding: 4,
        }}
      >
        <Typography variant="h3" sx={{ color: '#1976d2', mb: 2 }}>
          About Us
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ color: '#555', maxWidth: 800, textAlign: 'center' }}>
          JobWings connects job seekers with recruiters. Our platform provides tools for creating
          professional resumes, exploring jobs, and building a professional network.
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      <Box
        id="resume-templates"
        sx={{
          minHeight: '100vh',
          display: 'flex',
          flexDirection: 'column',
          alignItems: 'center',
          justifyContent: 'center',
          bgcolor: '#e3f2fd',
          padding: 4,
        }}
      >
        <Typography variant="h3" sx={{ color: '#1976d2', mb: 2 }}>
          Resume Templates
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ color: '#555', maxWidth: 800, textAlign: 'center' }}>
          Explore our wide range of professional resume templates tailored to different industries.
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      <Box
        id="jobs"
        sx={{
          minHeight: '100vh',
          display: 'flex',
          flexDirection: 'column',
          alignItems: 'center',
          justifyContent: 'center',
          bgcolor: '#fffde7',
          padding: 4,
        }}
      >
        <Typography variant="h3" sx={{ color: '#1976d2', mb: 2 }}>
          Jobs
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ color: '#555', maxWidth: 800, textAlign: 'center' }}>
          Browse job postings that match your skills and connect with recruiters directly.
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      <Box
        id="contact"
        sx={{
          minHeight: '100vh',
          display: 'flex',
          flexDirection: 'column',
          alignItems: 'center',
          justifyContent: 'center',
          bgcolor: '#e8f5e9',
          padding: 4,
        }}
      >
        <Typography variant="h3" sx={{ color: '#1976d2', mb: 2 }}>
          Contact Us
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ color: '#555', maxWidth: 800, textAlign: 'center' }}>
          Reach out to our support team for any assistance or inquiries.
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      {/* Footer */}
      <Box
        component="footer"
        sx={{
          bgcolor: '#1976d2',
          color: '#fff',
          py: 2,
          textAlign: 'center',
        }}
      >
        <Typography variant="body2" gutterBottom>
          © 2024 JobWings. All Rights Reserved.
        </Typography>
        <Box display="flex" justifyContent="center" gap={2}>
          <IconButton href="https://facebook.com" target="_blank" sx={{ color: '#fff' }}>
            <Facebook />
          </IconButton>
          <IconButton href="https://twitter.com" target="_blank" sx={{ color: '#fff' }}>
            <Twitter />
          </IconButton>
          <IconButton href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" sx={{ color: '#fff' }}>
            <Instagram />
          </IconButton>
        </Box>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Home;
